question: Is the value of patient 10021118's arterial blood pressure diastolic last measured on the first ICU visit greater than the second to last value measured on the first ICU visit?
true_query: SELECT ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10021118 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime ASC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'arterial blood pressure diastolic' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 ) > ( SELECT chartevents.valuenum FROM chartevents WHERE chartevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10021118 ) AND icustays.outtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY icustays.intime ASC LIMIT 1 ) AND chartevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'arterial blood pressure diastolic' AND d_items.linksto = 'chartevents' ) ORDER BY chartevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1 OFFSET 1 )

question: What was the prescription drug that patient 10004235 was prescribed for within the same hospital visit after receiving laparoscopic robotic assisted procedure since 03/2100?
true_query: SELECT T2.drug FROM ( SELECT procedures_icd.charttime, procedures_icd.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'laparoscopic robotic assisted procedure' ) AND procedures_icd.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10004235 ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100-03' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, prescriptions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id IN (SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10004235 ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',prescriptions.starttime) >= '2100-03' ) AS T2 ON T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime

question: What were the four most performed procedures for patients aged 20s?

question: In 2100, how many patients were given 0.9% sodium chloride (mini bag plus) in the same month after receiving a other endoscopy of small intestine procedure?

question: Give me the top five most frequent microbiology tests that patients received after dependence on respirator, status within the same month since 2100.

question: What are the top five most frequent specimens tested among patients who received destruction of right main bronchus, via natural or artificial opening endoscopic before within 2 months this year?

question: How much does the maximum total hospital cost include a procedure called combined right and left heart cardiac catheterization?

question: What are the three frequent lab tests for patients aged 20s since 1 year ago?

question: What is the 6-month survival rate for pneumonia due to klebsiella pneumoniae patients who were prescribed insulin after the diagnosis?
true_query: SELECT AVG(C1) FROM ( SELECT ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T3.charttime) < 1 * 365/2 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT T1.subject_id, T1.charttime FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'pneumonia due to klebsiella pneumoniae' ) AND strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/2 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'insulin' GROUP BY admissions.subject_id HAVING MAX(prescriptions.starttime) = prescriptions.starttime ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime ) AS T3 JOIN patients ON T3.subject_id = patients.subject_id )

question: Count the number of patients who received extracorporeal circulation auxiliary to open heart surgery during the same month after having been diagnosed with iatrogenic pneumothorax since 2100.
true_query: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT T1.subject_id ) FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'iatrogenic pneumothorax' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'extracorporeal circulation auxiliary to open heart surgery' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month')

question: Give me the top three most frequent diagnoses that patients were given within 2 months after receiving laparoscopic lysis of peritoneal adhesions since 1 year ago.
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'laparoscopic lysis of peritoneal adhesions' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3 )

question: Get me the top three most frequent lab tests that patients were given in the same hospital visit after being diagnosed with body mass index between 19-24, adult since 1 year ago.
true_query: SELECT d_labitems.label FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.itemid IN ( SELECT T3.itemid FROM ( SELECT T2.itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'body mass index between 19-24, adult' ) AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, labevents.itemid, labevents.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM labevents JOIN admissions ON labevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(labevents.charttime) >= datetime(current_time,'-1 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.itemid ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3 )

question: Get me the top five most frequent lab tests that patients had in the same month after receiving ultrasonography of superior vena cava, guidance in 2100.

question: What are the five most commonly used procedures for patients who had received drainage of peritoneal cavity, percutaneous approach, diagnostic previously within 2 months, in this year?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'drainage of peritoneal cavity, percutaneous approach, diagnostic' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )

question: What are the five most frequently tested specimens for patients who received extirpation of matter from left femoral vein, percutaneous approach previously within 2 months?

question: What is the top four most frequently prescribed drugs that were prescribed to patients within the same month after being diagnosed with other psoriasis in 2100?

question: What is the 3-month survival rate of patients who received alteplase treatment following a other psychotic disorder not due to a substance or known physiological condition diagnosis?
true_query: SELECT AVG(C1) FROM ( SELECT ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T3.charttime) < 1 * 365/4 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT T1.subject_id, T1.charttime FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'other psychotic disorder not due to a substance or known physiological condition' ) AND strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/4 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'alteplase' GROUP BY admissions.subject_id HAVING MAX(prescriptions.starttime) = prescriptions.starttime ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime ) AS T3 JOIN patients ON T3.subject_id = patients.subject_id )

question: Tell me the 6-month survival rate of patients who were diagnosed with microscopic hematuria and then given phytonadione.

question: What are the five most frequently ordered medications for patients diagnosed with gastro-esophageal reflux disease without esophagitis previously in the same hospital encounter, in 2100?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'gastro-esophageal reflux disease without esophagitis' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',prescriptions.starttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5

question: What were the top three frequent diagnoses that patients received during the same month after undergoing the resection of vessel with replacement, thoracic vessels procedure in 2100?

question: What are the five most frequently given diagnoses for the patients who had previously received laparoscopic partial cholecystectomy within 2 months, since 1 year ago?

question: Pull up the top four most frequent treatments that were delivered to patients during the same month after they received open reduction of fracture with internal fixation, humerus.

question: Could you tell me the top four most frequent treatments that were administered to patients during the same hospital encounter after they had fluoroscopy of right heart using other contrast since 2100?

question: Can I know the 3-month survival rate of patients diagnosed with subdural hemorrhage following injury without mention of open intracranial wound, with no loss of consciousness who were then prescribed phenobarbital?
true_query: SELECT AVG(C1) FROM ( SELECT ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T3.charttime) < 1 * 365/4 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT T1.subject_id, T1.charttime FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'subdural hemorrhage following injury without mention of open intracranial wound, with no loss of consciousness' ) AND strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/4 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'phenobarbital' GROUP BY admissions.subject_id HAVING MAX(prescriptions.starttime) = prescriptions.starttime ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime ) AS T3 JOIN patients ON T3.subject_id = patients.subject_id )

question: Tell me the total amount of solution that patient 10019917 had on 01/28/this year.
true_query: SELECT SUM(inputevents.totalamount) FROM inputevents WHERE inputevents.stay_id IN ( SELECT icustays.stay_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10019917 ) ) AND inputevents.itemid IN ( SELECT d_items.itemid FROM d_items WHERE d_items.label = 'solution' AND d_items.linksto = 'inputevents' ) AND datetime(inputevents.starttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m-%d',inputevents.starttime) = '01-28'

question: What were the four most commonly conducted lab tests during the same month for patients who had a other skin graft to other sites procedure during this year?
true_query: SELECT d_labitems.label FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.itemid IN ( SELECT T3.itemid FROM ( SELECT T2.itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'other skin graft to other sites' ) AND datetime(procedures_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, labevents.itemid, labevents.charttime FROM labevents JOIN admissions ON labevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE datetime(labevents.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.itemid ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )

question: When did since 02/2100 patient 10002495 receive a microbiology test for the last time?
true_query: SELECT microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents WHERE microbiologyevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10002495 ) AND strftime('%Y-%m',microbiologyevents.charttime) >= '2100-02' ORDER BY microbiologyevents.charttime DESC LIMIT 1

question: What were the microbiology tests that patient 10018845 had first received on the last hospital encounter?
true_query: SELECT microbiologyevents.test_name FROM microbiologyevents WHERE microbiologyevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10018845 AND admissions.dischtime IS NOT NULL ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC LIMIT 1 ) ORDER BY microbiologyevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1

question: Has there been any organism found in 06/this year in the first urine microbiology test of patient 10002495?
true_query: SELECT COUNT(*)>0 FROM microbiologyevents WHERE microbiologyevents.hadm_id IN ( SELECT admissions.hadm_id FROM admissions WHERE admissions.subject_id = 10002495 ) AND microbiologyevents.spec_type_desc = 'urine' AND microbiologyevents.org_name IS NOT NULL AND datetime(microbiologyevents.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') AND strftime('%m',microbiologyevents.charttime) = '06' ORDER BY microbiologyevents.charttime ASC LIMIT 1

question: Can you provide the top five most frequent lab tests that within the same month took place after patients had alcohol detoxification in 2100?
true_query: SELECT d_labitems.label FROM d_labitems WHERE d_labitems.itemid IN ( SELECT T3.itemid FROM ( SELECT T2.itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'alcohol detoxification' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, labevents.itemid, labevents.charttime FROM labevents JOIN admissions ON labevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',labevents.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.itemid ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 5 )

question: What drug was first prescribed to patient 10010471 via neb route since 12/2100?

question: What was patient 10004733's last prescription time of both iso-osmotic dextrose and vancomycin at the same time in this month?

question: How many days have gone by since the last instance patient 10039831 had a or colloid intake input in the current ICU encounter?

question: What was the name of a drug that patient 10005817 was prescribed within 2 days after being diagnosed with chronic airway obstruction, not elsewhere classified throughout this month?

question: Which five microbiology tests were most frequent for patients diagnosed with noncompliance with renal dialysis within 2 months?

question: What are the top five most frequent specimens tested among patients who received fluoroscopy of right heart using other contrast before within 2 months since 1 year ago?

question: In 2100, what were the top three most frequent lab tests conducted on patients during the same hospital encounter following a diagnosis of personal history of malignant neoplasm of other gastrointestinal tract?

question: What are the three most frequently tested specimens for patients who were previously diagnosed with encounter for attention to other artificial openings of digestive tract within 2 months?

question: How many patients in 2100 were lidocaine 5% patch prescribed during the same month after undergoing restriction of left internal carotid artery with intraluminal device, percutaneous approach treatment?

question: Can I know the 3-month survival rate of patients diagnosed with unspecified atrial fibrillation who were then prescribed rifaximin?
true_query: SELECT AVG(C1) FROM ( SELECT ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T3.charttime) < 1 * 365/4 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT T1.subject_id, T1.charttime FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'unspecified atrial fibrillation' ) AND strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/4 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'rifaximin' GROUP BY admissions.subject_id HAVING MAX(prescriptions.starttime) = prescriptions.starttime ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime ) AS T3 JOIN patients ON T3.subject_id = patients.subject_id )

question: What are the four commonly tested specimens for patients diagnosed with anoxic brain damage, not elsewhere classified previously during the same hospital visit, since 1 year ago?

question: What is the 6-month survival rate of patients who received insulin treatment following a personal history of poliomyelitis diagnosis?
true_query: SELECT AVG(C1) FROM ( SELECT ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T3.charttime) < 1 * 365/2 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT T1.subject_id, T1.charttime FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'personal history of poliomyelitis' ) AND strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/2 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'insulin' GROUP BY admissions.subject_id HAVING MAX(prescriptions.starttime) = prescriptions.starttime ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime ) AS T3 JOIN patients ON T3.subject_id = patients.subject_id )

question: Pull up the top three most frequent treatments that were delivered to patients in the same hospital visit after they received spinal tap.
true_query: SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'spinal tap' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.icd_code, procedures_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3 )

question: Could you provide me with the top four diagnoses associated with the highest 6-month mortality rate?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/2 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/2 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 4 )

question: What were the three most frequently prescribed medications for patients who were previously diagnosed with cardiogenic shock during the same month, since 2100?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'cardiogenic shock' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',prescriptions.starttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.starttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 3

question: For patients who took diagnostic ultrasound of digestive system , what are the top three most frequent specimens tested afterward within the same hospital visit?

question: What are the four diagnoses associated with the highest 3-month mortality rate?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/4 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/4 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 4 )

question: Was the SaO2 of patient 10007818 within the normal range on 07/08/this year?

question: What is the minimum monthly number of patient records marked with long-term (current) use of insulin?

question: How much is the diagnosis price for personal history of transient ischemic attack (tia), and cerebral infarction without residual deficits?

question: What are the top four frequent diagnoses that patients were diagnosed with since 2100 after having received a performance of cardiac output, continuous procedure within 2 months?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T3.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, procedures_icd.charttime FROM procedures_icd JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE procedures_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_procedures.icd_code FROM d_icd_procedures WHERE d_icd_procedures.long_title = 'performance of cardiac output, continuous' ) AND strftime('%Y',procedures_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T2.charttime) BETWEEN datetime(T1.charttime) AND datetime(T1.charttime,'+2 month') GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4 )

question: What is the count of patients who were diagnosed with constipation, unspecified in the same hospital visit after having been diagnosed with alcohol abuse, unspecified since 2100?
true_query: SELECT COUNT( DISTINCT T1.subject_id ) FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'alcohol abuse, unspecified' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'constipation, unspecified' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id

question: What are the four frequently prescribed drugs for patients who were diagnosed with mobitz (type) ii atrioventricular block previously in the same hospital encounter, in 2100?
true_query: SELECT T3.drug FROM ( SELECT T2.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'mobitz (type) ii atrioventricular block' ) AND strftime('%Y',diagnoses_icd.charttime) = '2100' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.starttime, admissions.hadm_id FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%Y',prescriptions.starttime) = '2100' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.starttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id GROUP BY T2.drug ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4

question: Can you list the top three most frequent treatments for patients aged 20s in 2100?

question: Give me the top four most frequent microbiology tests that patients received after ischemic cardiomyopathy during the same month.
true_query: SELECT T3.test_name FROM ( SELECT T2.test_name, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = ( SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'ischemic cardiomyopathy' ) ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, microbiologyevents.test_name, microbiologyevents.charttime FROM microbiologyevents JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND datetime(T1.charttime,'start of month') = datetime(T2.charttime,'start of month') GROUP BY T2.test_name ) AS T3 WHERE T3.C1 <= 4

question: Retrieve the top three drugs most frequently prescribed in the same hospital encounter to patients aged 50s post pulmonary collapse diagnosis.

question: Since 2100, what are the top three most frequent medications prescribed within the same hospital visit to patients in their 60 or above after they were diagnosed with esophageal reflux?

question: In the ptt lab test, what percentile does a value of 23.5 represent among patients of the same age as patient 10008287 in their last hospital encounter?

question: What were the top four most common lab tests that followed in the same hospital visit for patients who were given laryngoscopy and other tracheoscopy during this year?

question: What are the three diagnoses associated with the highest 6-month mortality rate?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/2 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/2 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 3 )

question: When did patient 10005909 first get prescribed for 0.9% sodium chloride and alteplase at the same time in 11/2100?
true_query: SELECT T1.starttime FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = '0.9% sodium chloride' AND admissions.subject_id = 10005909 AND strftime('%Y-%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '2100-11' ) AS T1 JOIN ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, prescriptions.starttime FROM prescriptions JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE prescriptions.drug = 'alteplase' AND admissions.subject_id = 10005909 AND strftime('%Y-%m',prescriptions.starttime) = '2100-11' ) AS T2 ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id WHERE datetime(T1.starttime) = datetime(T2.starttime) ORDER BY T1.starttime ASC LIMIT 1

question: Which are the four diagnoses with the highest 6-month mortality rate?
true_query: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/2 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/2 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 4 )

question: What are the five most commonly prescribed drugs for patients that received performance of urinary filtration, multiple previously within 2 months?

question: Since 2100, what were the three most frequent lab tests given to patients within the same month after they were diagnosed with body mass index (bmi) 32.0-32.9, adult?
